{
  "stem": "6763.4",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "If it's the last thing I do, I will get you.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "But he didn't.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "Uh.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "From there, we made arrangements-- excuse me-- to go to Ljubljana.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And we had friends.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And my father had left a stamp collection with some friends.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And they came to meet us, and they handed my father the albums of stamps.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "Then we took the train-- with the false papers, of course-- from Zagreb in the evening to Ljubljana.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "And it was almost like the country divided.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "Because at a certain point, it's Slovenia.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "The Slovenian border became Italy at that point.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "And I luxuriated in on the train, and I lied down, and I went to sleep.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "And I used the albums of the stamps as a cushion.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "And then I put whatever blanket on top of that and I went to sleep.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "And we arrived in Ljubljana and we were met by friends.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "And I mentioned my father had friends everywhere.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "And he corresponded with people all over the world forever.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And the first thing that these people asked us was, uh, Solo, whatever happened to your stamp collection?",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And obviously it was a very valuable stamp collection with a whole collection of Austria, which was very valuable.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And my father said, well, we have-- we have it with us.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they said, how did you get it across the border?",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I said, oh, I used it as a pillow and I slept on it.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And they said, did you realize there was a death penalty on this if you were caught?",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Even by the Italians, you would've been shot immediately.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Transporting a valuable stamp collection across the border, there was some kind of a death penalty on it.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So there are times when ignorance is bliss.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
